<div class="rt-article ">
	<div class="rt-article-bg">
		<div class="article-header">
											<h1 class="title">
				Biogas Combustion in Motorcycle Engine				</h1>
									
				
		</div>
		<div class="module-content">
					
						
					
			<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Turbulent Burning Velocity in Combustion Chamber<br />
	of SI Engine Fueled with Compressed Biogas&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></span></span><br />
	<br />
	<span style="color:#008000;">Bui Van Ga, Nguyen Van Dong, Bui Van Hung<br />
	<em>GATEC, University of Science and Technology, The University of Danang</em><br />
	<em> 
 <script language='JavaScript' type='text/javascript'>
 <!--
 var prefix = 'm&#97;&#105;lt&#111;:';
 var suffix = '';
 var attribs = '';
 var path = 'hr' + 'ef' + '=';
 var addy87939 = 'b&#117;&#105;v&#97;ng&#97;' + '&#64;';
 addy87939 = addy87939 + 'd&#111;ngc&#111;b&#105;&#111;g&#97;s' + '&#46;' + 'c&#111;m';
 document.write( '<a ' + path + '\'' + prefix + addy87939 + suffix + '\'' + attribs + '>' );
 document.write( addy87939 );
 document.write( '<\/a>' );
 //-->
 </script><script language='JavaScript' type='text/javascript'>
 <!--
